value: Extinct. Bred formerly on Funk Island off Newfoundland, on Iceland, the Faroes, St. Kilda and the Orkney Islands. Ranged southward on both sides of the North Atlantic to Massachusetts, the British Isles and Den- mark; casually to Florida and northern Spain.
refer: Peter's Checklist of the Birds of the World

value: Mostly at sea; nested on low coastal rocky islands.
